
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FarmAssist - Homepage</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            transition: 2s;

        }

        body:hover{
           
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f4f4f4; /* Change the background color */
    color: #333; /* Change the text color */
}
     .navbar{
      transition: 2s;
     }
      .navbar-brand:hover{
        font-weight: bolder;
        transform:scale(1.10)
      }
        .header {
            background-color: #4caf50;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        h5{
          margin-bottom: 0;
          margin-left: 1rem;
          margin-right: 1rem;
          padding: 5px 5px 5px 5px ;
        }
        h5:hover{
        background-color: #c5c5c5;
        color: black;
        align-items: center;
       
        
      }
      .nav-item:{
        transition: 1s;
      }

        .content {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .nav-item:hover{
          background-color: #4caf50;
          color: white;
          border-radius: 5px;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .animated {
            animation: fadeIn 1s;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        

        h2 {
            color: #4caf50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        marquee.announcement {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  white-space: nowrap;
  overflow: hidden;
  animation: marqueeAnimation 10s linear infinite;
  
}
    .badge{
      background-color: #4caf50;
    }
    .hvr:hover{
      font-weight: bolder;
      transform: translateX(5px);
    }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
            <div class="container-fluid">
              <a href="/"><img src="1.png" width="120" height="60" style="margin: 0rem 1rem;" class="d-inline-block align-top" alt=""></a>
              
          
              <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                  <li class="nav-item" class="hvr">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/" class="hvr">Home</a>
                  </li>
                  <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/aboutus">About Us</a>
                  </li>
                  <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/schemes">Get Popular Schemes</a>
                  </li>
                  <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/news">Explore News</a>
                  </li>
                  <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/contactus">Contact Us</a>
                  </li>
                  <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/getschemes">Personalized Schemes</a>
                  </li>
                </ul>
                    <h5 style="font-weight:light;transition:1s; height:40px; width:fit-content;text-align:center;border-radius:5px;align-items:center;justify-content:center">Welcome,  {{#if userName}}{{userName}}{{else}}Guest{{/if}}!</h5>

              </div>
            </div>
          </nav>
          <marquee class="announcement" direction="">Pune Agricultural Summit 2024 is coming soon!! <span class="badge badge-success">NEW</span>
</marquee>
    </header>
     <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.10.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-7+zCNj/IqJ95wo16oMtfsKbZ9ccEh31eOz1HGyDuCQ6wgnyJNSYdrPa03rtR1zdB" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-QJHtvGhmr9XOIpI6YVutG+2QOK9T+ZnN4kzFN1RtK3zEFEIsxhlmWl5/YESvpZ13" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>